Do not show the startup window.
.TP
.B
\fB--verbose-sound-init\fP
Display more info about the sound setup.
.TP
.B
\fB--no-sound\fP
Do not play any sounds. Instead some data is printed
to standard output. Use this for debugging and
porting.
.TP
.B
\fB--debug\fP
